Therefore, broadcasted binary operations involving `x` and `y` can be performed.

&nbsp;

Now let's look at another 2 arrays, and see if they are compatible:



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
x <- array(rnorm(10), c(10, 1, 9, 6))
y <- array(rnorm(10), c(10, 5, 2))
